0593.topic&index=21>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: So...its been about 3 months now since the change to Vul</span><hr size=1> Personally, i think NTOV's power level was pretty much where it needed to be.  I think that some of the items, specifically vulak loot, was absurd for that power level though.<br>
<br>
