<br>
The rest of NTOV is very good.  Its challenging.  The item rewards are between balanced, to a little high. But vulak loot was absolute insanity for the encounter.  With basic strategy worked out, any guild with a reasonable amount of capability could kill that version of vulak.<br>
<br>
Now if vulak is spawned once a month, instead of once a week (or more, thx patches), at least that loot isnt the primary source of mudflation.  This assumes the script eventually starts working =p<br>
<br>
Finally, changing the rest of ntov is not the answer.  It was already done once, and I think that was enough.<br>
<br>
